snippet.title: Demon Slayer -Kimetsu no Yaiba- The Hinokami Chronicles 2 | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Become the blade that destroys demons in Demon Slayer - Kimetsu no Yaiba - The Hinokami Chronicles 2!

Coming to PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Steam, and Nintendo Switch in 2025.
